OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FPep Guardiola could step down as
OL,7,FManchester City boss at the end of the
OL,8,Fseason, with the FA Cup winners not
OL,9,Fcommenting on a fresh report that the
OL,10,FSpaniard will depart this summer.
OL,12,FThe 55-year-old, who has won 20
OL,13,Ftrophies during 10 golden years at the
OL,14,FEtihad Stadium, is revered as one of
OL,15,Fthe greatest managers of the Premier
OL,16,FLeague era.
OL,18,FBut who are the possible contenders
OL,19,Fwho could be brave enough to replace
OL,20,Fhim?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
