OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FEnzo Maresca
OL,8,FFormer Leicester and Chelsea boss Enzo
OL,9,FMaresca has emerged as the bookmakers'
OL,10,Fearly favourite.
OL,12,FThe 46-year-old Italian has twice had
OL,13,Fstints as part of Guardiola's coaching
OL,14,Fstaff at City, latterly as assistant
OL,15,Fmanager in 2022 before leading
OL,16,FLeicester to top-flight promotion in
OL,17,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
