OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FHe lifted the Conference League trophy
OL,7,Fwith Chelsea in 2025, but departed
OL,8,FStamford Bridge after a breakdown in
OL,9,Frelations with the club's owners at
OL,10,Fthe turn of the year.
OL,12,FBayern Munich head coach Kompany also
OL,13,Ffeatures high on the bookies' list.
OL,15,FThe 40-year-old former City skipper
OL,16,Fspent a trophy-laden nine years at the
OL,17,Fclub as a player. After beginning his
OL,18,Fmanagerial career at Anderlecht, he
OL,19,Fled Burnley to Premier League
OL,20,Fpromotion in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
