OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FAfter the Clarets were relegated the
OL,7,Ffollowing season, he was appointed as
OL,8,FThomas Tuchel's successor at Bayern,
OL,9,Fwho he has led to back-to-back
OL,10,FBundesliga titles.
OL,12,FLuis Enrique
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
