OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old Spaniard enjoyed a
OL,7,Fstellar playing career with Real
OL,8,FMadrid and Barcelona and has also
OL,9,Fspent time in charge of his country,
OL,10,Falbeit without success. But he has
OL,11,Fbeen a serial trophy winner during
OL,12,Fspells in charge of Barca and at
OL,13,Fcurrent club Paris St Germain, with
OL,14,Fwhom he has won three straight Ligue 1
OL,15,Ftitles.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
