OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FLuis Enrique delivered Champions
OL,7,FLeague glory last season for the first
OL,8,Ftime in their history and they will
OL,9,Fbid to defend their European crown in
OL,10,Fthe final later this month against
OL,11,FArsenal.
OL,13,FAndoni Iraola
OL,15,FAnother Spaniard, the 43-year-old will
OL,16,Fbe a free agent in summer having
OL,17,Fannounced last month his intention to
OL,18,Fstep down as Bournemouth manager at
OL,19,Fthe end of the season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
