PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779279069
OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FIraola has worked wonders with the
OL,7,FCherries, leading them to a 12th-
OL,8,Fplaced Premier League finish in 2025
OL,9,Fand to the brink of European football
OL,10,Ffor the fist time in their history as
OL,11,Fthey currently sit sixth in the table
OL,12,Fand still in contention for a
OL,13,FChampions League place.
OL,15,FCesc Fabregas
OL,17,FThe former Arsenal midfielder's place
OL,18,Fon the list highlights further the
OL,19,Fabundance of world-class Spanish
OL,20,Fmanagers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
