OL,3,CFive contenders who could replace Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola at Manchester City
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old former Spain
OL,7,Fmidfielder twice won the Premier
OL,8,FLeague at Chelsea as a player and a
OL,9,FLaLiga crown with Barcelona.
OL,11,FHis managerial career is in its early
OL,12,Fstages, but he helped Como to top-
OL,13,Fflight promotion as an assistant in
OL,14,F2024 and, after taking sole charge,
OL,15,Fhas guided them to at least a place in
OL,16,Fthe Europa League this season, while
OL,17,Fthey could still qualify for the
OL,18,FChampions League.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
